      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Semantic Zoom\n\nStatus: partially implemented for this phase.\n\nFocus state, fragment-relative semantic levels, and bullseye-safe authority are now real. The next layer is to make nearby graph structure come alive more automatically without letting authority roam.",
