    {
      "id": "task-node-class-contract-semantic-zoom",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Node-Class Contract",
      "position": {
        "x": -620,
        "y": 80
      },
      "width": 460,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Representation Contract\n\nTwilite needs two related representation families:\n\n## Node-level (for node instances)\n- `node.web.detail`\n- `node.web.summary`\n- `node.web.icon`\n\n## Graph-level (for graphs rendered as objects)\n- `graph.web.detail`\n- `graph.web.summary`\n- `graph.web.icon`\n\nLegacy `node.web` should imply detail. Normal full-graph rendering remains the fallback for the canvas role.\n\nA class graph may define both families, but a node instance still resolves through `node.*`, not `graph.*`.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T01:20:00.000Z"
          },
          "intent": "graph",
          "meaning": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "defaults": {},
          "nodeDef": {
            "key": "markdown",
            "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
            "source": "local",
            "version": ">=0.1.0"
          },
          "views": [
            {
              "key": "markdown",
