    {
      "id": "task-renderer-contract-semantic-zoom",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Renderer Contract",
      "position": {
        "x": -80,
        "y": 80
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Renderer Contract\n\nThe renderer should:\n\n1. Identify the current focused node/fragment\n2. Resolve a semantic base level for the focused fragment\n3. Render linked fragments at relative lower levels\n4. Apply physical zoom as a secondary constraint\n5. Avoid cases where peripheral fragments are more detailed than the focused fragment\n\nThis should be runtime-driven and deterministic.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
