    {
      "id": "task-fragments-groups-semantic-zoom",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Fragments & Groups",
      "position": {
        "x": 920,
        "y": 80
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Graph Contexts\n\nSemantic zoom applies to linked `.node` graphs as navigation contexts, but the same graph can be rendered in different roles.\n\n- as canvas: active graph workspace\n- as graph-object: represented inside another graph\n\nGroups and clusters can later inherit the same model, but the first-class concern is graph context rendered by role and level.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
