    {
      "id": "task-phases-semantic-zoom",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Implementation Phases",
      "position": {
        "x": -620,
        "y": 460
      },
      "width": 460,
      "height": 360,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Implementation Phases\n\n## Phase 1\nAdd focus state and focused-fragment base level resolution.\n\n## Phase 2\nAdd fragment-relative semantic levels (`detail` / `summary` / `icon`).\n\n## Phase 3\nUse the bullseye to auto-expand direct linked graph/document targets in browse mode while keeping authority fragment-scoped.\n\n## Phase 4\nSupport richer authored semantic representations and fallback logic.\n\n## Phase 5\nAdd polish: transitions, layout-aware behavior, and override controls.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
