    {
      "id": "task-focus-state-contract-semantic-zoom",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Focus State Contract",
      "position": {
        "x": 1820,
        "y": -260
      },
      "width": 440,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Focus State Contract\n\nFocus should be runtime-only state.\n\nSuggested shape:\n\n- `focusedNodeId`\n- `focusedFragmentId`\n- `origin` (`navigation`, `expand`, `embed`, `manual`, `history`)\n- `updatedAt`\n\n`focusedFragmentId` is the semantic zoom anchor and is derived from the fragment containing `focusedNodeId`.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
