    {
      "id": "task-focus-triggers-semantic-zoom",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Focus Triggers",
      "position": {
        "x": 1820,
        "y": 100
      },
      "width": 440,
      "height": 340,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Focus Triggers\n\nFragment focus should change only on explicit navigation events:\n\n- navigate via port\n- expand fragment\n- enter embedded graph\n- explicit focus action\n- history back/forward\n\nIt should **not** change on:\n\n- selection only\n- drag\n- hover\n- property edits\n- marquee selection\n- pan / zoom\n\nThat keeps semantic priority stable.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
