    {
      "id": "task-base-level-resolver-semantic-zoom",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Base Level Resolver",
      "position": {
        "x": 2320,
        "y": -260
      },
      "width": 460,
      "height": 340,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Base Level Resolver\n\nThe runtime must resolve the current semantic level for the focused fragment before computing relative fragment levels.\n\nSuggested levels:\n\n- `detail`\n- `summary`\n- `icon`\n\nThe resolver sets the base level for the focused fragment. Linked fragments then step down relative to that level.",
        "_classBinding": {
