    {
      "id": "task-resolver-inputs-semantic-zoom",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Resolver Inputs",
      "position": {
        "x": 2320,
        "y": 140
      },
      "width": 460,
      "height": 360,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Resolver Inputs\n\nRecommended inputs for the focused fragment base level:\n\n- `viewportZoom`\n- `semanticLock`\n- `isEditing`\n- `isInteracting`\n\nPriority order:\n\n1. explicit semantic lock\n2. active editing override\n3. active interaction override\n4. physical zoom bands\n5. default fallback\n\nGraph distance should *not* affect the base level. Distance is applied after the base level is chosen.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
