    {
      "id": "task-interaction-overrides-semantic-zoom",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Interaction Overrides",
      "position": {
        "x": 2320,
        "y": 980
      },
      "width": 460,
      "height": 360,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Interaction Overrides\n\nThe focused fragment should resist over-compression while the user is actively working in it.\n\nInitial rules:\n\n- if editing inside the focused fragment: minimum base level = `detail`\n- if actively navigating/interacting: minimum base level = `summary`\n- otherwise defer to zoom-band resolution\n\nThis prevents the focused fragment from collapsing below what the current interaction justifies.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
