    {
      "id": "task-rendering-role-semantic-zoom",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Rendering Role",
      "position": {
        "x": 2840,
        "y": 140
      },
      "width": 460,
      "height": 340,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Rendering Role\n\nRepresentation resolution should depend on both:\n\n- semantic level\n- rendering role\n\nSuggested roles:\n\n- `canvas` for the active graph workspace\n- `graph-object` for a graph represented inside another graph\n- `node` for ordinary node views\n\nThis prevents the runtime from confusing `show me this graph` with `show me something about this graph`.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
