    {
      "id": "task-role-level-resolution-semantic-zoom",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Role + Level Resolution",
      "position": {
        "x": 2840,
        "y": 560
      },
      "width": 460,
      "height": 360,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Role + Level Resolution\n\nRepresentation should be resolved by a combination of role and semantic level.\n\nExamples:\n\n- active graph + canvas role -> normal graph renderer\n- linked graph + graph-object role + summary level -> graph summary representation\n- linked graph + graph-object role + icon level -> graph icon representation\n- ordinary node + node role + detail level -> node detail view\n\nRole chooses the representation family. Semantic level chooses the representation variant.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
