    {
      "id": "task-automatic-semantic-fallback-semantic-zoom",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Automatic Semantic Fallback",
      "position": {
        "x": 3880,
        "y": -260
      },
      "width": 480,
      "height": 360,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Automatic Semantic Fallback\n\nSemantic zoom should work by default, even when extra semantic views are not authored.\n\nRules:\n\n- missing `node.web.summary` falls back automatically\n- missing `node.web.icon` falls back automatically\n- missing `graph.web.summary` derives automatically\n- missing `graph.web.icon` derives automatically\n\nAuthored semantic views should improve the result, not be required for the system to function.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
