    {
      "id": "task-structural-automatic-fallback-semantic-zoom",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Structural Automatic Fallback",
      "position": {
        "x": 4400,
        "y": -260
      },
      "width": 500,
      "height": 360,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Structural Automatic Fallback\n\nAutomatic graph-object representations should be structural reductions, not content summaries.\n\nThey should use plain graph data only:\n\n- manifest identity\n- manifest description\n- manifest intent\n- graph counts\n- source/ref metadata\n\nThey should not depend on AI, interpretation, or deep content mining.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
