    {
      "id": "task-identity-over-meaning-semantic-zoom",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Identity Over Meaning",
      "position": {
        "x": 4400,
        "y": 180
      },
      "width": 500,
      "height": 340,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Identity Over Meaning\n\nAutomatic semantic fallback should summarize **identity and scale**, not **meaning**.\n\nGood automatic signals:\n\n- graph title\n- graph description\n- node/edge counts\n- graph kind/scope\n\nMeaningful or domain-rich summaries belong in authored semantic views, not in automatic fallback.",
        "_classBinding": {
