    {
      "id": "task-automatic-graph-object-drawing-policy-semantic-zoom",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Automatic Drawing Policy",
      "position": {
        "x": 4400,
        "y": 580
      },
      "width": 500,
      "height": 400,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Automatic Drawing Policy\n\nSuggested baseline object ladder:\n\n## automatic detail\n- graph icon\n- title\n- short description\n- counts row\n\n## automatic summary\n- graph icon\n- title\n- minimal subtitle or count strip\n\n## automatic icon\n- graph glyph\n- short label or count badge\n\nThis gives predictable reduction without defeating the purpose of summarization.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
