    {
      "id": "task-representation-cache-scope-semantic-zoom",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Representation Cache Scope",
      "position": {
        "x": 4920,
        "y": -260
      },
      "width": 500,
      "height": 340,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Representation Cache Scope\n\nCache only resolved semantic representation data.\n\nCache candidates:\n\n- derived graph-object detail\n- derived graph-object summary\n- derived graph-object icon\n- resolved explicit-vs-derived representation choice\n\nDo **not** cache active canvas rendering, focus state, viewport state, or mounted UI.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
