    {
      "id": "task-cache-keys-semantic-zoom",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Cache Keys",
      "position": {
        "x": 4920,
        "y": 160
      },
      "width": 500,
      "height": 340,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Cache Keys\n\nCache keys should be deterministic and small.\n\nSuggested key:\n\n`target + role + level + revision`\n\nWhere:\n\n- `target` = graph/class identity\n- `role` = `node` or `graph-object`\n- `level` = `detail`, `summary`, `icon`\n- `revision` = in-memory version token for the underlying source\n\nIf revision changes, the cache entry is stale by definition.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
