      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Invalidation Rules",
      "position": {
        "x": 4920,
        "y": 580
      },
      "width": 500,
      "height": 360,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Invalidation Rules\n\nInvalidate cached semantic representations when:\n\n- graph nodes/edges/groups change\n- manifest identity/description/intent changes\n- authored semantic views change\n- class/view definitions change\n\nDo **not** invalidate just because focus, selection, panning, or physical zoom changed. Those affect which representation is requested, not whether the cached representation is stale.",
