    {
      "id": "task-in-memory-only-phase1-semantic-zoom",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "In-Memory Only (Phase 1)",
      "position": {
        "x": 4920,
        "y": 1020
      },
      "width": 500,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# In-Memory Only (Phase 1)\n\nPhase 1 caching should be in-memory only.\n\n- no localStorage\n- no IndexedDB\n- no file persistence\n\nUse a simple runtime `Map` keyed by representation identity. Extend later only if performance data justifies it.",
