    {
      "id": "task-explicit-sticky-focus-semantic-zoom",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Explicit Sticky Focus",
      "position": {
        "x": 5440,
        "y": -260
      },
      "width": 500,
      "height": 360,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Explicit Sticky Focus\n\nFocused node/fragment should be set primarily by explicit navigation events, not by geometry.\n\nFocus should be **sticky**:\n\n- click / navigate / expand / enter embed sets focus\n- focus persists until explicitly changed or invalidated\n- panning and zooming alone do not change focus\n\nThis keeps semantic zoom stable and intentional.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
