    {
      "id": "task-viewport-center-fallback-semantic-zoom",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Viewport Center Fallback",
      "position": {
        "x": 5440,
        "y": 180
      },
      "width": 500,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Viewport Center Fallback\n\nViewport-center heuristics should be fallback only.\n\nUse them only when:\n\n- no focus currently exists\n- the previous focus became invalid\n- a replacement focus must be chosen\n\nEven then, center-of-viewport should be treated as a recovery heuristic, not the normal driver of semantic focus.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
