    {
      "id": "task-no-focus-churn-semantic-zoom",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "No Focus Churn On Pan/Zoom",
      "position": {
        "x": 5440,
        "y": 580
      },
      "width": 500,
      "height": 340,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# No Focus Churn On Pan/Zoom\n\nSemantic zoom must not reassign focus just because the camera moved.\n\nRules:\n\n- pan does not change focus\n- zoom does not change focus\n- focus is only reassigned on explicit navigation or invalidation\n\nThis prevents accidental radical representation changes when the user is only reframing the viewport.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
