    {
      "id": "task-browse-vs-edit-modes-semantic-zoom",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Browse vs Edit Modes",
      "position": {
        "x": 5960,
        "y": -260
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 360,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Browse vs Edit Modes\n\nTwilite needs to distinguish navigation intent from editing intent.\n\n- **browse mode**: focus, navigate, expand, inspect\n- **edit mode**: select, drag, resize, rewire, mutate\n\nThis keeps focus and selection from competing for the same mouse gesture. Semantic zoom belongs primarily to browse behavior.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
