        "markdown": "# Toolbar Mode Switch\n\nWhen the full editor toolbar is present, the user should have an explicit mode switch:\n\n- `Browse`\n- `Edit`\n\nThe switch must change event interpretation, not just appearance. This makes intent explicit and keeps the interaction model understandable.",
