    {
      "id": "task-mode-specific-mouse-semantics-semantic-zoom",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Mode-Specific Mouse Semantics",
      "position": {
        "x": 5960,
        "y": 920
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 380,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Mode-Specific Mouse Semantics\n\nSuggested first-pass behavior:\n\n## browse mode\n- click = focus\n- navigation affordance = open / traverse\n- semantic zoom follows navigation\n\n## edit mode\n- click = select\n- drag = move\n- resize/connect/edit enabled\n\nThe same gesture should not mean both \"focus this\" and \"edit this\" at the same time.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T01:20:00.000Z"
          },
          "intent": "graph",
          "meaning": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "defaults": {},
          "nodeDef": {
            "key": "markdown",
            "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
            "source": "local",
            "version": ">=0.1.0"
          },
          "views": [
            {
