    {
      "id": "task-pointer-primary-navigation-semantic-zoom",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Pointer-Primary Navigation",
      "position": {
        "x": 6480,
        "y": -260
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Pointer-Primary Navigation\n\nGraph navigation in Twilite should be pointer-primary.\n\nMouse/pointer input is the main way to:\n\n- focus graph objects\n- traverse references\n- expand branches\n- inspect graph context\n\nThis matches the spatial nature of the medium.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
