    {
      "id": "task-no-arrow-key-graph-browsing-semantic-zoom",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "No Arrow-Key Graph Browsing",
      "position": {
        "x": 6480,
        "y": 560
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# No Arrow-Key Graph Browsing\n\nArrow keys are not a sufficient model for graph navigation.\n\nThey are too linear and too ambiguous for a spatial, branching workspace.\n\nKeyboard navigation should only update focus when tied to an explicit navigation command, not via generic arrow-key browsing.",
