    {
      "id": "task-initial-focus-resolution-semantic-zoom",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Initial Focus Resolution",
      "position": {
        "x": 7000,
        "y": -260
      },
      "width": 540,
      "height": 360,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Initial Focus Resolution\n\nOn initial graph load:\n\n1. find the first root node\n2. set it as `focusedNodeId`\n3. set the containing graph context as `focusedFragmentId`\n\nFallback order:\n\n- first explicit root node\n- first visible node\n- `null` only if the graph is empty\n\nThis gives semantic zoom a deterministic startup anchor.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
