      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Fragment Layout Dependency\n\nSemantic zoom depends on fragment layout policy when multiple expanded fragments are visible.\n\nSemantic zoom can decide:\n\n- focus\n- relative representation level\n- visual prominence\n\nBut layout determines:\n\n- where fragments appear\n- how they avoid overlap\n- whether adjacency is legible\n- whether semantic hierarchy reads clearly\n\nThis remaining issue belongs at the boundary between semantic zoom and fragment layout.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
